Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.80,0:00:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I pledge to clean up Japan once and for all."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.77,0:00:11.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now then, whose line was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:13.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.25,0:00:15.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew I've heard it somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.27,0:00:16.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.61,0:00:18.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakamoto Ryouma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.11,0:00:24.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They say on June 29th in Year 3 of Bunkyuu, or 1863...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:28.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ryouma wrote that in a letter he addressed to his elder sister, Otome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:31.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sure know a lot, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:34.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I heard on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.21,0:00:39.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Sonoko, why are you quoting Ryouma?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.34,0:00:46.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a Ryouma exhibition that's been held at Uncle Jirokichi's Suzuki Grand Museum since last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:50.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the guy who sent out an advance notice of attendance is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.06,0:00:52.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None other than my dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitou Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.23,0:00:56.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Twas him, zeyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:00.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Zeyo"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.19,0:01:01.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.32,0:01:02.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You spoke in a Tosa dialect...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.99,0:01:05.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's exactly it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.03,0:01:07.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was studying up on Ryouma, and I totally got into his dialect!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:09.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:13.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think there's anything at the Ryouma exhibition that Kid would want to steal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.31,0:01:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course there is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.58,0:01:19.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the gunbelt Ryouma is said to have received from Takasugi Shinsaku along with a pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.42,0:01:20.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gunbelt!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:23.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.05,0:01:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a magnificent belt with a huge ruby embedded in the buckle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.72,0:01:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.72,0:01:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ryouma even wrote about that belt in a letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.89,0:01:37.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we have a certificate of authenticity from a famous appraiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:39.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, why wouldn't it be real?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.65,0:01:42.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jirokichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} bought it, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.15,0:01:44.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I heard he wasn't able to acquire it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.95,0:01:50.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person planning to put on the exhibition with the belt as a centerpiece...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:52.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't seem to want to sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.91,0:01:56.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Having no choice, Uncle said, "If you're going to have a Ryouma exhibition, have it at my museum!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.71,0:01:58.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And lent him the space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:03.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But further proof is that Kid is targeting it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:04.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually he isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.97,0:02:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:12.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like fog clearing up in a swoosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.17,0:02:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see through both romance and cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:16.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An advance notice different than usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:17.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fierce battle for treasures against Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:19.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:21.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:10.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,CONAN & KID'S BATTLE FOR
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:10.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,RYOUMA'S TREASURE (PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:12.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's coming to return some stolen items?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did Kid really write that in his advance notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:19.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:23.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"In the Ryouma exhibition, which is being held now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:28.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I shall make a visit with the purpose of returning three items in a few days."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Kaitou Kid."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What three items?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:36.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems the organizer of the Ryouma exhibition, Tarumi Shishihiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:39.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Had also held another Ryouma exhibition 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:42.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some items were stolen at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:45.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A letter written by Sakamoto Ryouma the night before he was assassinated...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:49.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Addressed to his wife, Oryou, although unfinished...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:54.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A sake cup from Oumiya Inn stained with Ryouma's blood upon his death...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:05:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And finally, a pistol Ryouma had hidden under his clothes, a Smith & Wesson Model 1, these three items.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:05.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, those items weren't stolen by Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:06.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:07.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:11.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nicknamed the Shouwa Era's Woman of Twenty Faces...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:13.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the damsel thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:14.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Phantom Lady"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:19.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't know what kind of relationship Kid and Lady have.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:22.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But after stealing the three items, the Lady ceased her crimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:26.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And two years later Kid made his appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:29.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From this we can assume they may be master and apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:31.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:33.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When is that guy coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:34.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't say anything other than "in a few days" in the notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:41.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, we should stop the Ryouma exhibition now and turn away the visitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:45.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the time and date are uncertain, our security will be at a disadvantage and that's what his aim is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he's just returning things, it'll be easy for him to slip into the crowd!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:52.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But here's the thing, Nakamori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:56.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't he saying he's coming all the way to return things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why should we refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:06:00.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, but Superintendent...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:05.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, if we want to apprehend Kid, don't we have to invite him first?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suzuki Jirokichi who received the notice also said this:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:13.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Make the entrance large and the exit narrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:16.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the basics for catching a rat!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:19.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Suzuki Grand Museum
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:19.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:20.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:23.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, since that time with the Iron Tanuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:25.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:28.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's quite a crowd of visitors lined up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:29.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:34.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In addition to the popularity of Ryouma, they also heard about Kid's notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:37.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, if I were in charge of the exhibition...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would have flooded the newspapers and TV stations with ads...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.91,0:06:43.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And gathered a crowd several times this size!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't this rare?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:53.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For Uncle to lend out space in the museum for someone else's exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:56.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't intend to at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:07:02.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since I learned Kid would be after it, I knew I couldn't leave it up to amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amateurs?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:03.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:08.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man behind this exhibition named Tarumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Had also held the ones for Yoshitsune and Nobunaga...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whenever there's a boom for historical figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But because of lax security, something always gets stolen by unidentified thieves each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you should've bought it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:24.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Ryouma's gunbelt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:26.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was the price too unreasonable?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, on the contrary, I haggled down the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:34.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, he wouldn't allow me to show it to my appraiser before buying it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I couldn't ascertain its authenticity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:41.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But didn't you get a certification from a well-known appraiser?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:43.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:47.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I felt uneasy about whether or not it'd be able to hook Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:50.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Kid did take the bait, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:54.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though his target doesn't seem to be the gunbelt...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:08:00.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tarumi Shishihiko (58)\NRyouma Exhibition Organizer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That gunbelt is without a doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:08:01.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The genuine thing received by Ryouma from Takasugi Shinsaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Hanamura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:11.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanamura Masanosuke (63)\NAppraiser
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:05.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:10.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Based on the condition of the leather, it is undoubtedly an antique.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ruby in the buckle is also superb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, Ryouma even drew an illustration of the belt in his missive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am thus compelled to declare it genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:22.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanamura Masanosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:27.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His judgment is tried and true, but his appraisal fees are exorbitant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:30.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's an appraiser who rarely takes on any jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:36.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, why don't you ladies also come and see the genuine articles with your own eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:39.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The exhibition hasn't started yet, but it's my special treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:46.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is Ryouma's gunbelt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:48.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It gives off a certain je ne sais quoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:51.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there really is a picture of the belt in this letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you can't read the words...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:09:03.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"This here is a gunbelt from ages gone, worn around the waist by American men...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:10.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"'Twas used to carry their pistols and bullets, akin to a sash holding a scabbard...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:17.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"As to why none of the present New Yorkers don such an engrossing and convenient article...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:20.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"'Tis to me an utterly mystifying observation."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:21.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:24.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It does sound like Ryouma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:25.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zeyo, zeyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:30.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that gigantic vase?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:35.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:41.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The vase that Ryouma was said to have hidden in as a child when playing hide-and-seek but got stuck in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:47.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We also have the Buddha statue Ryouma praised after observing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:49.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And a ball-and-cup toy Ryouma yearned for on display.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So everything goes, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:55.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this hanging scroll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:10:01.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the scroll he wrote without thinking as he lamented the depravity of the shogunate system.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:02.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:05.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I still have doubts about its authenticity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you lack confidence in my eyes to that extent...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:16.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then after the Ryouma exhibition is concluded, you are welcome to show these to your own appraiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that is my intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:23.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, that's provided you are able to keep these items away from that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Magician of the Moonlight's devilish grasp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:32.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, I appreciate your assistance with the museum's security, Advisor Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:32.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a pair of shady folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:43.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it possible that the items on display are insured for a lot of money?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also suspected that and looked into it, but the amount is only a drop in the bucket.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:55.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With even the admission fee being low, should anything get stolen he is bound to suffer substantial losses, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.33,0:10:56.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.73,0:10:58.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How will you play your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:01.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean your must have preparations, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To counter Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:04.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did practically nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:11.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:12.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Right," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he were coming to steal something, I would've thought of ideas to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:21.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since he's coming to return things, there's no way to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:26.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention all three items are small and can easily slip under his clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:30.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the best I could do was create that space.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:36.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Spaced Reserved for Kaitou Kid's Returned Treasures," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we at least knew what time and day he was coming, we could take some sort of measures, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:42.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:45.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he didn't write when he was coming in his notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:54.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though Kid's never before sent out a notice that didn't specify a time or date, or at least a hint about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:56.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:12:00.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, could it be that it's a copycat pretending to be Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:05.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that manifesto definitely came from that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.61,0:12:11.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet he intends to send another notice with the time and date after he sees an opportunity, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:15.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like, maybe his schedule is full and he's waiting until it's convenient for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we assume that to be true...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:20.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What in the world is he waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected, a huge turnout!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:48.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the most popular spot is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:52.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Spaced Reserved for Kaitou Kid's Returned Treasures"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:53.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ryouma must be crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't push me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They put sensors only on that space...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:22.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they let police officers mix in with the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:24.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:26.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was only playing a prank...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:31.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, I'm terribly sorry and I regret my actions, so please forgive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:32.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that anyone who takes suspicious actions gets intervened immediately, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:33.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Advisor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is bad, Advisor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this boisterousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was just delivered ro your house in the mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:46.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:48.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid's manifesto?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:55.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow at 20:00 when the museum closes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shall bring the pistol and the other items...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:01.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And in the name of the Bakumatsu patriot, Sakamoto Ryouma...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:05.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I pledge to clean up once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:06.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitou Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:15.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,KID!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:16.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:18.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Clean up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:20.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:22.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:29.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was Kid waiting for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:50.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I pledge to clean up once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:51.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:56.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Conan Episode 627\NFansub Release bt DCTP\NOCR: Nixx Car\NOCR Editing: DJ VK
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take notice of this long line of spectators!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.51,0:15:06.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Having heard that Kaitou Kid has announced his arrival time as 20:00 tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:13.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One after another, Kid fans are descending on the Suzuki Grand Museum despite it having just closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:16.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will Kid really be able to return per his announcement...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.61,0:15:23.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Sakamoto Ryouma's letter, sake cup, and pistol that were stolen 20 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:28.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And will he feel inclined to appropriate Ryouma's gunbelt as a reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:32.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, what is the motive behind his sudden reveal of the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:35.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will everything be made clear tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:38.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rain, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean Kid waited until it was going to rain before choosing his arrival time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:45.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:48.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's going to rain any moment now outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:50.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the weather report for tomorrow also said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.23,0:15:54.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how does that guy intend to utilize the rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:59.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does he plan to break in through the ceiling of this exhibition room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:00.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:07.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have my staff check every day before we open, but nothing resembling explosives had been set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could his plan pertain to the visitors' clothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:12.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.96,0:16:16.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's raining, many people will be wearing ponchos or raincoats.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:21.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he wears rain gear, it would be easy to blend into the crowd!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:22.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zeyo, zeyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:27.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really doubt Kid would have such a trifling reason to wait for rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:33.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But nonetheless, we should halt the Ryouma exhibition and turn away the visitors tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, Kid will have no choice but to waltz into the exhibition room where we're guarding...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the purpose of returning the three items all by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:48.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be the perfect situation in which to capture him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:55.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, that guy always disguises himself as you or your subordinates...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.39,0:16:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or uses sleeping gas to knock you out in that situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:16:59.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:17:06.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we equip everyone with gas masks and constantly have them confirm each other with passwords, we'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:11.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the bothersome visitors out of the way, we'll be sure to nab him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:14.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I fear that we cannot endorse such a strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:18.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did go through the trouble of gathering items related to Sakamoto Ryouma...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And organizing this Ryouma exhibition for visitors to see, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:30.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How would it look if you blockaded the exhibition for an entire day simply because of a single thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:33.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:37.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, during the case of his teleportation...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:42.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard he almost stopped his criminal performance because the crowd was locked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.01,0:17:49.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't he coming to return those three items that were stolen from me 20 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:52.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd be quite upset if it were suspended.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, please allow the guests to enter as usual tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.94,0:18:02.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whether Kid is caught or not depends solely upon your competence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In addition, there is something we'd like you to carefully guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:13.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After Kid returns those three items, he intends to steal the highlight of this Ryouma exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.95,0:18:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Namely...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:19.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Ryouma's gunbelt as his reward, or so did the rumors say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:22.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we do have faith...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:24.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In you police officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:26.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:29.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you have faith in us, you should cooperate, I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:31.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With so many visitors, it'll be easy for him to return the three items.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.77,0:18:39.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know a way that can deter him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.31,0:18:43.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, it's written on the advance notice you received, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:51.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Tomorrow at 20:00 when the museum closes, I shall bring the pistol and the other items.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:54.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"And in the name of the Bakimatsu patriot, Sakamoto Ryouma...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I pledge to clean up once and for all."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:18:59.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.55,0:19:04.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because instead of stealing things like usual, Kid is returning things this time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:06.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And one of those is a pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.44,0:19:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So if we install a metal detecting gate like they have at airports and check everyone, we'd expose him right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the one carrying the pistol will be Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:20.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.42,0:19:22.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you're so smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We police already thought about installing that, but the higher ups stopped us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:31.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:36.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we were to protect things from being stolen, we'd put one at the museum entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:41.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they fear if he sees that kind of thing before entering the museum, he might end up not returning the items.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:48.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead of at the museum entrance, why don't we put the gate in front of the Ryouma exhibition room?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can install a lot so the visitors can move more smoothly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:55.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a genius idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:20:00.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And while we're at it, we can perfect the plan by setting up X-ray machines to scan the contents of handbags!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:02.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:04.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know Kid's coming tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:07.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way you could prepare those in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.92,0:20:08.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the power of my Suzuki Financial Group, it's a guaranteed cakewalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:16.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we can capture that guy with the gates, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if anyone turns tail and retreats due to the gates, we will know that's Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:23.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:26.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Begin setting up the gates immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:32.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have an entire night to turn this museum into a gargantuan Anti-Kid mousetrap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:32.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:38.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected, rich men enjoy doing flashy things...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's also the possibility that Kid brought the pistol into the building ahead of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Use metal detectors to check every nook and cranny of this museum!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:21:00.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Next Day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.83,0:21:05.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To the officer guarding the museum entrance, how's the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:06.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:09.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have not yet observed any guests quickly turning tail after seeing the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:13.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Any problems at the metal detectors?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:14.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There have been no guests with a pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.56,0:21:19.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And in the exhibition room?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At this time, there is no one resembling Kid in the premises.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.89,0:21:25.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But is Kid really coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.00,0:21:30.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid's never failed to show up any time he's made an announcement!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:31.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.11,0:21:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How, come forth, Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:38.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time, I swear I'll apprehend you once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:42.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.29,0:21:46.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They really made it look like the airport terminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention there are even three gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.17,0:21:50.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's Uncle for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.63,0:21:51.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:21:58.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something still bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.05,0:22:03.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he deliberately wrote in his notice that he's "bring the pistol and the other items"...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.77,0:22:06.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course he should've been able to predict that things would turn out this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.73,0:22:12.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's more, I still haven't figured out how he intends to use the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.44,0:22:18.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I don't get the meaning behind the last sentence of the notice, "I pledge to clean up once and for all."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.87,0:22:23.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was he merely trying to be clever by using Ryouma's words?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.58,0:22:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or is there something he truly intends to clean up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.42,0:22:30.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What on earth is Kid's aim?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.05,0:24:23.94,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.56,0:24:03.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seventeen centimeters would be about...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.06,0:24:06.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roughly this size?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.84,0:24:07.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.87,0:24:11.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time I only came to return the stolen items.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.58,0:24:13.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go in too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.23,0:24:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it'd be better if you didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.90,0:24:19.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it seems Kid really is going to clean up in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.64,0:24:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitou Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.03,0:24:30.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,CONAN & KID'S BATTLE FOR RYOUMA'S TREASURE\N(PART TWO)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.55,0:24:48.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.09,0:24:50.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watercolor Paint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.11,0:24:54.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look Forward to the Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.46,0:24:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm planning to return the treasures this time, so don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.10,0:24:54.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't bet on it!
